{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I had a fire nine days ago."},{"time":5000,"text":"My archive:"},{"time":7000,"text":"175 films, my 16-millimeter negative,"},{"time":10000,"text":"all my books, my dad's books, my photographs."},{"time":13000,"text":"I'd collected --"},{"time":15000,"text":"I was a collector, major, big-time."},{"time":17000,"text":"It's gone."},{"time":20000,"text":"I just looked at it,"},{"time":22000,"text":"and I didn't know what to do."},{"time":25000,"text":"I mean, this was --"},{"time":27000,"text":"was I my things?"},{"time":30000,"text":"I always live in the present -- I love the present."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"I cherish the future."},{"time":36000,"text":"And I was taught some strange thing as a kid,"},{"time":39000,"text":"like, you've got to make something good out of something bad."},{"time":41000,"text":"You've got to make something good out of something bad."},{"time":43000,"text":"This was bad! Man, I was --"},{"time":45000,"text":"I cough. I was sick."},{"time":47000,"text":"That's my camera lens. The first one --"},{"time":49000,"text":"the one I shot my Bob Dylan film with 35 years ago."},{"time":52000,"text":"That's my feature film. \"King, Murray\""},{"time":54000,"text":"won Cannes Film Festival 1970 --"},{"time":56000,"text":"the only print I had."},{"time":59000,"text":"That's my papers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61000,"text":"That was in minutes -- 20 minutes."},{"time":63000,"text":"Epiphany hit me. Something hit me."},{"time":65000,"text":"\"You've got to make something good out of something bad,\""},{"time":69000,"text":"I started to say to my friends, neighbors, my sister."},{"time":71000,"text":"By the way, that's \"Sputnik.\" I ran it last year."},{"time":73000,"text":"\"Sputnik\" was downtown, the negative. It wasn't touched."},{"time":77000,"text":"These are some pieces of things I used in my Sputnik feature film,"},{"time":80000,"text":"which opens in New York in two weeks"},{"time":82000,"text":"downtown."},{"time":86000,"text":"I called my sister. I called my neighbors. I said, \"Come dig.\""},{"time":88000,"text":"That's me at my desk."},{"time":92000,"text":"That was a desk took 40-some years to build."},{"time":94000,"text":"You know -- all the stuff."},{"time":96000,"text":"That's my daughter, Jean."},{"time":98000,"text":"She came. She's a nurse in San Francisco."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100000,"text":"\"Dig it up,\" I said. \"Pieces."},{"time":102000,"text":"I want pieces. Bits and pieces.\""},{"time":104000,"text":"I came up with this idea: a life of bits and pieces,"},{"time":107000,"text":"which I'm just starting to work on -- my next project."},{"time":109000,"text":"That's my sister. She took care of pictures,"},{"time":112000,"text":"because I was a big collector of snapshot photography"},{"time":115000,"text":"that I believed said a lot."},{"time":117000,"text":"And those are some of the pictures that --"},{"time":119000,"text":"something was good about the burnt pictures."},{"time":121000,"text":"I didn't know. I looked at that --"},{"time":123000,"text":"I said, \"Wow, is that better than the --\""},{"time":125000,"text":"That's my proposal on Jimmy Doolittle. I made that movie for television."},{"time":127000,"text":"It's the only copy I had. Pieces of it."},{"time":131000,"text":"Idea about women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133000,"text":"So I started to say, \"Hey, man, you are too much!"},{"time":136000,"text":"You could cry about this.\" I really didn't."},{"time":139000,"text":"I just instead said,"},{"time":141000,"text":"\"I'm going to make something out of it, and maybe next year ... \""},{"time":143000,"text":"And I appreciate this moment"},{"time":145000,"text":"to come up on this stage with so many people"},{"time":147000,"text":"who've already given me so much solace,"},{"time":150000,"text":"and just say to TEDsters:"},{"time":152000,"text":"I'm proud of me. That I take something bad,"},{"time":155000,"text":"I turn it, and I'm going to make something good out of this,"},{"time":157000,"text":"all these pieces."},{"time":159000,"text":"That's Arthur Leipzig's original photograph I loved."},{"time":162000,"text":"I was a big record collector --"},{"time":164000,"text":"the records didn't make it. Boy, I tell you,"},{"time":166000,"text":"film burns. Film burns."},{"time":169000,"text":"I mean, this was 16-millimeter safety film."},{"time":171000,"text":"The negatives are gone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174000,"text":"That's my father's letter to me, telling me to"},{"time":176000,"text":"marry the woman I first married when I was 20."},{"time":180000,"text":"That's my daughter and me."},{"time":184000,"text":"She's still there. She's there this morning, actually."},{"time":186000,"text":"That's my house."},{"time":188000,"text":"My family's living in the Hilton Hotel in Scotts Valley."},{"time":191000,"text":"That's my wife, Heidi,"},{"time":193000,"text":"who didn't take it as well as I did."},{"time":196000,"text":"My children, Davey and Henry."},{"time":199000,"text":"My son, Davey, in the hotel two nights ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203000,"text":"So, my message to you folks,"},{"time":205000,"text":"from my three minutes, is that I appreciate the chance"},{"time":208000,"text":"to share this with you. I will be back. I love being at TED."},{"time":211000,"text":"I came to live it, and I am living it."},{"time":214000,"text":"That's my view from my window outside of Santa Cruz, in Bonny Doon,"},{"time":217000,"text":"just 35 miles from here."},{"time":220000,"text":"Thank you everybody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}